  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 70ee8ab7554a13a4d9d7566ffc03ae8b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Returning the Favor
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FlightPaper.ProjectSorrow.Encounters.EncounterScriptableObject
  id: 9
  title: Returning the Favor
  description: 'You bump into your buddy in the crowd.


    He tells you he''s going
    to grab something from the food trucks outside. Since you spotted him some money
    last time, he offers to buy you something.'
  options:
  - title: Ask for some chips
    description: Earn <color=#00C300>Salt & Vinegar Chips</color>
    requirement: Requires an available consumable slot
    conclusion: '"Alright if that''s all you want."


      When he returns with
      your chips, he thanks you for spotting him last time. The two of you discuss
      your last performance, and he wishes you the best of luck. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 11400000, guid: bcf67907b94d3dc46a0a733c5bd0b42a, type: 2}
    tag: 
  - title: Ask for a burger
    description: Earn <color=#00C300>Smash Burger</color>
    requirement: Requires an available consumable slot
    conclusion: '"Just like you usually like it, right?"


      After a little time,
      he returns with two fresh burgers from outside. You take in the aroma of what
      will surely be the greasiest burger you''ve had in a long time. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1190e7b31f491b144b47a8dfd8a42350, type: 2}
    tag: 
  - title: Ask for some tacos
    description: Earn <color=#00C300>Fish Tacos</color>
    requirement: Requires an available consumable slot
    conclusion: '"Alright, fish tacos are on the way."


      He returns a short
      time later with your tacos and a pair of tacos of his own. The two of you catch
      up a bit while you have the time. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a310fb11748e51f42a1fc9c6c3d10b59, type: 2}
    tag: 
  - title: Ask for your money back
    description: <color=green>+$5</color>, <color=red>-2</color> reputation
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'You see the excitement leave his face. "Sure. I was just trying
      to return the favor."


      After he hands you the money, there''s an awkward
      silence between you. You try to make some small talk, but the conversation
      is short lived before he leaves. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: Reputation
  minRound: 0
